description: A dozen children fly from overcrowded camps to Luxembourg - the first of 1,600 Europe is to host.
title: Greece relocates unaccompanied migrant children to Luxembourg
title_page: Greece relocates unaccompanied migrant children to Luxembourg - BBC News
maintext: There are about 100,000 asylum seekers in Greece, most of whom are in camps, hotel rooms and flats. So far there have been two outbreaks in camps on the Greek mainland.
